    <div class="content"><p>The last hotel I stayed in (at F2C) had trouble keeping +Ethernet cables+ in hotel rooms.  Unless there's a way to cement them to the wall, they'll get stolen.  </p>
<p>The cable in two rooms was broken, and the manager said that people try to steal them even though they have a bulky plastic paperweight / ad attached to them.</p>
</div>
