    <div class="content"><p>Unless someone carries USB cables without data pins, this would be a great way to steal guests personal data.  Cars are starting to have USB ports instead of "12vdc outlets" (former cigarette lighters), also a good target for this.</p>
<p>Regardless of that, I agree.  Good idea.  Paranoids can carry non-data cables.</p>
